<li data-marker"24." id="note24">
<p data-aid="141537341" id="note24_p1">See <a class="scripture-ref" href="/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/128.8?lang=eng#p8">Doctrine and Covenants 128:8</a>; see also <a class="scripture-ref" href="/study/scriptures/ot/ex/19.5-6?lang=eng#p5">Exodus 19:5&#x2013;6</a>; <a class="scripture-ref" href="/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.40?lang=eng#p40">Doctrine and Covenants 84:40</a>. Those who worthily keep covenants become a precious treasure, a kingdom of priests, a holy nation. Covenants sanctify. Those who keep covenants become sanctified to the Lord.</p>
